Some guns are kinda hidden, in not only the darkness, but in nooks and crannies. xP so good luck finding em' all.
I advise having flashlights enabled, not required though, just as fun without.

Things hidden well : GALIL, FAMAS, hegrenade, scout, AWP, UMP45, DEagle.
Not much to say right now, I suppose I'll say more when it's done. ^ ^
